<%= render partial: "shared/header", locals: {tab: @virtual_path[/^[^\/]+/]} %>

<div class="giant-sections">

  <div class="giant-section">
    <div class="giant-section-title">
      <h2>What We Offer Candidates</h2>
    </div> <!-- /giant-section-title -->
    <div class="giant-cluster">
      <div class="giant-cluster-item">
        <h4>THE RIGHT POSITION</h4>
        <p>We listen to you. We believe in listening to our candidates
          to find out what they want and matching them with the
          position that’s right for them.</p>
      </div> <!-- /giant-cluster-item -->
      <div class="giant-cluster-item">
        <h4>COMPENSATION INSIGHT</h4>
        <p>We know our stuff. Our data is your data - we’ll advise you
          on market rates and compensation to make sure you get
          paid what you’re worth.</p>
      </div> <!-- /giant-cluster-item -->
    </div> <!-- /giant-cluster -->
    <div class="giant-cluster">
      <div class="giant-cluster-item">
        <h4>ADVICE AND CONSULTATION</h4>
        <p>We’ll guide you. Job searching can be tough, that’s why
          our expereinced recruiting team will lend a helping hand
          - whether it be advising you on your resume, portfolio or
          how to approach your job hunt.</p>
      </div> <!-- /giant-cluster-item -->
      <div class="giant-cluster-item">
        <h4>UNDERSTANDING EMPLOYER'S NEEDS</h4>
        <p>We get them. Because we have a deep understanding of
          what our clients need, the team at Giant will make sure
          we’re connecting you with the right opportunity that will
          help advance your career and skillset.</p>
      </div> <!-- /giant-cluster-item -->
    </div> <!-- /giant-cluster -->
    <div class="giant-cluster">
      <div class="giant-cluster-item">
        <h4>INTERVIEW PREPARATION</h4>
        <p>We’ve got your back. We work closely with hiring
          managers and hiring teams, giving us valuable insight
          into their interview process. We’ll prep you before your
          interview and give you all the tools you need to land your
          dream job.</p>
      </div> <!-- /giant-cluster-item -->
      <div class="giant-cluster-item">
        <h4>PROACTIVE PLACEMENTS</h4>
        <p>We don’t wait around. Even if we don’t have an open job
          that’s a fit, we’ll proactively seek employers and
          opportunities for you that are a fit with your background
          and career objectives.</p>
      </div> <!-- /giant-cluster-item -->
    </div> <!-- /giant-cluster -->
    <div class="giant-section-title">
      <%= render partial: "shared/button_open_jobs" %>
    </div> <!-- /giant-section-title -->
  </div> <!-- /giant-section -->

  <div class="giant-section-separator"></div>

  <div class="giant-section">
    <div class="giant-testimonial">
      <blockquote>
        “Giant Recruiting team is amazing! They are great at
        communicating and getting results. Always available
        for questions and advice. I have worked with them on
        several freelance gigs and would highly recommend
        anyone thinking of using a professional recruiter to
        contact Giant Recruiting!!”
      <footer><cite>
        FREELANCE, ART DIRECTOR
      </cite></footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div> <!-- /giant-testimonial -->
  </div> <!-- /giant-section -->

</div> <!-- /giant-sections -->

<%= render partial: "shared/footer" %>
